## getDataContract

**Returns**: [Data Contract](explanation-platform-protocol-data-contract) information for the requested data contract
**Parameters**:

| Name | Type | Required | Description |
| - | - | - | - |
| `id` | Bytes | Yes | A data contract `id` |

** Example Request and Response **
[block:code]
{
  "codes": [
    {
      "code": "const DAPIClient = require('@dashevo/dapi-client');
const Identifier = require('@dashevo/dpp/lib/Identifier');
const cbor = require('cbor');

const client = new DAPIClient();

const contractId = Identifier.from('6Ti3c7nvD1gDf4gFi8a3FfZVhVLiRsGLnQ7nCAF74osi');
client.platform.getDataContract(contractId).then((response) => {
  const contract = cbor.decode(response);
  console.dir(contract, { depth:10 });
});",
      "language": "javascript",
      "name": "JavaScript (dapi-client)"
    },
    {
      "code": "const {
